32#ifndef SINGLEAPPLICATION_P_H
33#define SINGLEAPPLICATION_P_H
34
35#include <QtCore/QSharedMemory>
36#include <QtNetwork/QLocalServer>
37#include <QtNetwork/QLocalSocket>
38#include "singleapplication.h"
39
40struct InstancesInfo {
41 bool primary;
42 quint32 secondary;
43 qint64 primaryPid;
44 quint16 checksum;
45 char primaryUser[128];
46};
47
48struct ConnectionInfo {
49 qint64 msgLen = 0;
50 quint32 instanceId = 0;
51 quint8 stage = 0;
52};
53
54class SingleApplicationPrivate : public QObject {
55Q_OBJECT
56public:
57 enum ConnectionType : quint8 {
58 InvalidConnection = 0,
59 NewInstance = 1,
60 SecondaryInstance = 2,
61 Reconnect = 3
62 };
63 enum ConnectionStage : quint8 {
64 StageHeader = 0,
65 StageBody = 1,
66 StageConnected = 2,
67 };
68 Q_DECLARE_PUBLIC(SingleApplication)
69
70 SingleApplicationPrivate( SingleApplication *q_ptr );
71 ~SingleApplicationPrivate() override;
72
73 QString getUsername();
74 void genBlockServerName();
75 void initializeMemoryBlock();
76 void startPrimary();
77 void startSecondary();
78 void connectToPrimary(int msecs, ConnectionType connectionType );
79 quint16 blockChecksum();
80 qint64 primaryPid();
81 QString primaryUser();
82 void readInitMessageHeader(QLocalSocket *socket);
83 void readInitMessageBody(QLocalSocket *socket);
84
85 SingleApplication *q_ptr;
86 QSharedMemory *memory;
87 QLocalSocket *socket;
88 QLocalServer *server;
89 quint32 instanceNumber;
90 QString blockServerName;
91 SingleApplication::Options options;
92 QMap<QLocalSocket*, ConnectionInfo> connectionMap;
93
94public Q_SLOTS:
95 void slotConnectionEstablished();
96 void slotDataAvailable( QLocalSocket*, quint32 );
97 void slotClientConnectionClosed( QLocalSocket*, quint32 );
98};
99
100#endif // SINGLEAPPLICATION_P_H
